{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5c34c71b41","title":"中央军委关于新疆奎屯农校武斗事件的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"42d0ca4f25","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":31,"articleId":"5c34c71b41","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"边境地区和少数民族","id":"c0cd6cf1d4","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央军委文件","id":"d125b2a9b6","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"通讯","id":"d5cbd05390","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"11a9d2285a","type":"title","text":"中央军委关于新疆奎屯农校武斗事件的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c34c71b41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa7906c76c","type":"paragraph","text":"新疆军区、新疆生产建设兵团并转奎屯驻军：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c34c71b41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b420287838","type":"paragraph","text":"据报告，农七师农校发生严重武斗，红战团于今日攻占了红旗兵团三百余人所固守的大楼，人员下落、伤亡情况不明，请你立即指定专人，对此事进行妥善处理。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c34c71b41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"652dd68ce6","type":"paragraph","text":"1、绝对保证红旗兵团三百多人的人身安全，不准以任何借口对他们进行迫害，不准逮捕同情和支持他们的群众。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c34c71b41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2d8c4dbc3b","type":"paragraph","text":"2、对伤员要妥善治疗。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c34c71b41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"045e03bb98","type":"paragraph","text":"3、对双方要做好政治工作，坚决执行中央《六·六》通令。各群众组织之间，如有不同意见通过协商解决，要坚决制止武斗。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c34c71b41","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90739ff1ed","type":"paragraph","text":"4、上述处理结果和双方伤亡的数字迅速上报。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5c34c71b41","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}